    "export_view": {
      "value": "<h2 id=\"Qpop\u2122CompanionRecommendedImageResolutions-RecommendedImageResolutions\">Recommended Image Resolutions</h2><p>A user with the Location Admin role or higher can add/edit Qpop devices, and a user with Shift Lead or higher can pair and launch Qpop Companion.\u00a0The below measurements are in pixels.</p><h3 id=\"Qpop\u2122CompanionRecommendedImageResolutions-AdditionalResources\">Additional Resources</h3><ul><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1936523288/Qpop+Companion+System+Requirements\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1936523288\" data-linked-resource-version=\"8\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Qpop\u2122 Companion System Requirements</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1937047567/Qpop+Companion+Resources+with+Video\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1937047567\" data-linked-resource-version=\"13\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Qpop\u2122 Companion Resources</a></p></li></ul><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1936261206/image-20230608-180314.png?api=v2\"></span><h3 id=\"Qpop\u2122CompanionRecommendedImageResolutions-iPad9.7&quot;(Non-RetinaModels)\">iPad 9.7&quot; (Non-Retina Models)</h3><p>Welcome/Idle Screen: 1024w x 768h<br/>Ticket Summary: 512w x 768h</p><h3 id=\"Qpop\u2122CompanionRecommendedImageResolutions-iPadMini7.9&quot;\">iPad Mini 7.9&quot;</h3><p>Welcome/Idle Screen: 1024w x 768h<br/>Ticket Summary: 512w x 768h</p><h3 id=\"Qpop\u2122CompanionRecommendedImageResolutions-iPad9.7&quot;(RetinaModels)\">iPad 9.7&quot; (Retina Models)</h3><p>Welcome/Idle Screen: 2048w x 1536h<br/>Ticket Summary: 1024w x 1536h</p><h3 id=\"Qpop\u2122CompanionRecommendedImageResolutions-iPadMini7.9&quot;.1\">iPad Mini 7.9&quot;</h3><p>Welcome/Idle Screen: 2048w x 1536h<br/>Ticket Summary: 1024w x 1536h</p><h3 id=\"Qpop\u2122CompanionRecommendedImageResolutions-iPadPro9.7&quot;\">iPad Pro 9.7&quot;</h3><p>Welcome/Idle Screen: 2048w x 1536h<br/>Ticket Summary: 1024w x 1536h</p><h3 id=\"Qpop\u2122CompanionRecommendedImageResolutions-iPadPro12.9&quot;\"><br/>iPad Pro 12.9&quot;</h3><p>Welcome/Idle Screen: 2732w x 2048h<br/>Ticket Summary: 1366w x 2048h</p><h3 id=\"Qpop\u2122CompanionRecommendedImageResolutions-SamsungGalaxyTabS8.4&quot;\"><br/>Samsung Galaxy Tab S 8.4&quot;</h3><p>Welcome/Idle Screen: 2560w x 1600h<br/>Ticket Summary: 1280w x 1600h</p><h3 id=\"Qpop\u2122CompanionRecommendedImageResolutions-SamsungGalaxyTabS2/3\"><br/>Samsung Galaxy Tab S2/3</h3><p>Welcome/Idle Screen: 2048w x 1536h<br/>Ticket Summary: 1024w x 1536h</p><h3 id=\"Qpop\u2122CompanionRecommendedImageResolutions-SamsungGalaxyTabA9.7&quot;\"><br/>Samsung Galaxy Tab A 9.7&quot;</h3><p>Welcome/Idle Screen: 1024w x 768h<br/>Ticket Summary: 512w x 768h</p><h3 id=\"Qpop\u2122CompanionRecommendedImageResolutions-SamsungGalaxyTabA10.1&quot;\"><br/>Samsung Galaxy Tab A 10.1&quot;</h3><p>Welcome/Idle Screen: 1920w x 1200h<br/>Ticket Summary: 960w x 1200h</p><p /><p /><p>START 1.18.X</p>",
